snippet.title: Java Final Keyword Tutorial - Learn Final Variables, Methods and Classes
snippet.description:
New course coming soon! Learn Java Fast launches on July 1st, 2020. Stay informed and join the waitlist: https://course.alexlorenlee.com/courses/learn-java-fast

- The final keyword in java means it doesn't change. You set it once and if you want to change it again, you can't. This is useful for global variables or anything you know will never change.

I hope this helps you use the final keyword in your java programs, I know I didn't have a solid understanding of the final keyword when I was in college. 

I hope you enjoyed this java final keyword tutorial! -

Free tips and programs: http://alexlorenlee.com
